Changed [phrase_arch.py](/Users/anthony/Programming/PromptClaw/src/cypherclaw/render/rules/phrase_arch.py) to support per-phrase arc profiles: explicit `PerformanceIntent`/metadata `arc_shape` wins, explicit rule `arc_shape` remains supported, otherwise shape is sampled from intent-weighted authored distributions with peak variance. Withhold can now select `flat`, and flat profiles set `tempo_deviation_pct` to `0.0`.

